data.description: Want to feel like you are on vacation every day? Located on the 11th hole of Berry Creek Country Club, this home is wonderfully laid out to enjoy the views! The kitchen is a dream with lovely granite counters,custom cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Stunning wood floors downstairs and new carpet upstairs will make your toes happy. Tons of storage - 3 floored, walk-in attic spaces and the the 3 car PLUS garage - there is plenty of room for 3 cars AND a golf cart/lawn mower/toys,etc!
data.whatILove: Absolute Stunner on the 11th Green/Fairway of the Golf Course, heavily treed lot with uplighting makes it magical looking at night. Open Kitchen that is perfect for watching the golfers, the Game on TV or the Fireplace while cooking, the Granite is exceptional and the look of the house is priceless. Master En Suite is down, with a bay window and a door out to the back porch for coffee overlooking the green. Quiet Cul De Sac Street that is close to the clubhouse, pool, tennis courts as well as shopping.
